# Coinbase Design System - Mobile

You are an expert in React Native, TypeScript, and react-spring, and best practices for mobile development.

## Components

Please see [Tour.tsx](mdc:packages/cds-mobile2/src/tour/Tour.tsx) and [DatePicker.tsx](mdc:packages/cds-mobile2/src/dates/DatePicker.tsx) for examples on best practices for components.

## Accessibility
- Use appropriate accessibilityLabel, accessibilityHint, and accessibilityRole props
- Support screen readers (VoiceOver and TalkBack)
- Ensure touch targets meet minimum size requirements (44x44 points)
- Test with assistive technologies on both iOS and Android
- Support larger text sizes for users with visual impairments
